/*Megachan CSS v1.0.18*/

.megachan svg:not(:root),.sr-only{overflow:hidden}
body,html{min-height:100%}
#megachan,.ps{display:block;height:82px;margin-bottom:22px;-webkit-font-smoothing:antialiased;-moz-osx-font-smoothing:grayscale}
#megachan:after,#megachan:before,.ps:after,.ps:before{display:table;content:''}
#megachan:after,.ps:after{clear:both}
#megachan .container,.ps .container{position:relative;padding:0}
#megachan .container .row,.ps .container .row{margin:0;display: block}
.chan-hidden{display:none!important}
.chan-visible{display:inline-block!important}
.chan-pull-right{float:right!important}
.sr-only{position:absolute;width:1px;height:1px;padding:0;margin:-1px;clip:rect(0,0,0,0);border:0}
.megachan:focus{outline:dotted thin!important;outline-offset:0!important}
@media screen and (max-width:767px) {
#megachan .container,.ps .container{display:none}
#classicMobile{display:block}
#megachan,.ps{height:44px!important;margin-bottom:auto!important}
}
@media screen and (min-width:768px) {
#megachan .container,.ps .container{display:block;width:970px;margin:0 auto}
#classicMobile{display:none}
}
@media screen and (min-width:992px) {
#megachan .container,.ps .container{width:970px!important}
}
.megachan html{font-family:sans-serif;-ms-text-size-adjust:100%;-webkit-text-size-adjust:100%}
.megachan body{margin:0}
.megachan article,.megachan aside,.megachan details,.megachan figcaption,.megachan figure,.megachan footer,.megachan header,.megachan hgroup,.megachan main,.megachan menu,.megachan nav,.megachan section,.megachan summary{display:block}
.megachan audio,.megachan canvas,.megachan progress,.megachan video{display:inline-block;vertical-align:baseline}
.megachan audio:not([controls]){display:none;height:0}
.megachan [hidden],.megachan template{display:none}
.megachan a:active,.megachan a:hover{outline:0}
.megachan abbr[title]{border-bottom:1px dotted}
.megachan b,.megachan strong{font-weight:700}
.megachan dfn{font-style:italic}
.megachan h1{font-size:2em;margin:.67em 0}
.megachan mark{background:#ff0;color:#000}
.megachan small{font-size:80%}
.megachan sub,.megachan sup{font-size:75%;line-height:0;position:relative;vertical-align:baseline}
.megachan sup{top:-.5em}
.megachan sub{bottom:-.25em}
.megachan img{border:0}
.megachan figure{margin:1em 40px}
.megachan hr{box-sizing:content-box;height:0}
.megachan pre{overflow:auto}
.megachan code,.megachan kbd,.megachan pre,.megachan samp{font-family:monospace,monospace;font-size:1em}
.megachan button,.megachan input,.megachan optgroup,.megachan select,.megachan textarea{color:inherit;font:inherit;margin:0}
.megachan button{overflow:visible}
.megachan button,.megachan select{text-transform:none}
.megachan button,.megachan html input[type=button],.megachan input[type=reset],.megachan input[type=submit]{-webkit-appearance:button;cursor:pointer}
.megachan button[disabled],.megachan html input[disabled]{cursor:default}
.megachan button::-moz-focus-inner,.megachan input::-moz-focus-inner{border:0;padding:0}
.megachan input{line-height:normal}
.megachan input[type=checkbox],.megachan input[type=radio]{box-sizing:border-box;padding:0}
.megachan input[type=number]::-webkit-inner-spin-button,.megachan input[type=number]::-webkit-outer-spin-button{height:auto}
.megachan input[type=search]{-webkit-appearance:textfield;box-sizing:content-box}
.megachan input[type=search]::-webkit-search-cancel-button,.megachan input[type=search]::-webkit-search-decoration{-webkit-appearance:none}
.megachan fieldset{border:1px solid silver;margin:0 2px;padding:.35em .625em .75em}
.megachan legend{border:0;padding:0}
.megachan textarea{overflow:auto}
.megachan optgroup{font-weight:700}
.megachan table{border-collapse:collapse;border-spacing:0}
.megachan td,.megachan th{padding:0}

.megachan nav.primary-chan .level-1{position:absolute;margin:0;padding:0;bottom:0;font-size:0}
.megachan nav.primary-chan .level-1 .megachan-dropdown&gt;h2:after{color:#999;transform-origin:center;border-style:solid;border-width:.14em .14em 0 0;content:'';display:inline-block;height:.55em;position:relative;width: 0.55em;transform:rotate(135deg);right:5px;bottom:6px;margin:-4px;box-sizing:border-box;}

0%{opacity:0}
to{opacity:1}
}
@keyframes b {

to{opacity:1}
